<section class="intro-slide" id="intro-slide-digital-strategy">
  <div class="intro-slide__content">
    <h2 class="intro-slide__heading">Digital land. Held like gold.</h2>
    <p class="intro-slide__subtitle">
      We buy and hold digital assets as a long-term store of value.
    </p>

    <ul class="intro-slide__benefits">
