          West anymore.
        </span>
      </li>
    </ul>
    <p class="intro-slide__source">
      Sources: BitGo (OCC national trust bank) · Lloyd's of London · public filings of BlackRock,
      Fidelity, BNY Mellon, Bank of America
    </p>
  </div>
